songs.title: Running Back To Me
songs.lyrics:
We had our moments. We had our fights. We had the nights were I slept on the coach while you slept in the kitchen. But worst of all, you've cheated multiple times and I'm faded. Now you see me gone. Now you see how tired I was of you
So don't be, coming back to me. After seeing how I am. Cause I hope you know my response
No, don't be running back to me. I don't wanna be, your lover. No, I don't wanna see you anymore. I don't wanna play your games



CAUTION:THIS IS A LEAKED VERSE AND PART OF A CHORUS OFF HER UPCOMING ALBUM WHICH IS BEING DEBATED TO BE TITLED BETWEEN Selena or Lose You To Love Me. THIS WILL BE TRACK 5-10 AND WILL TITLED Running Back To Me
